OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784906303
OL,3,CPolice officer arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof rape
OL,6,FA serving police officer with Durham
OL,7,FConstabulary has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of rape.
OL,10,FThe force has said that upon his
OL,11,Farrest earlier this month, the officer
OL,12,Fwas immediately suspended from duty.
OL,14,FA criminal investigation is now
OL,15,Funderway, being led by the force's
OL,16,FProfessional Standards Department.
OL,18,FThe arrested officer has since been
OL,19,Freleased on bail while the
OL,20,Finvestigation continues.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
