PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784906303
OL,3,CPolice officer arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof rape
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Independent Office for
OL,7,FPolice Conduct (IOPC) has confirmed
OL,8,Fthat it has received a referral from
OL,9,FDurham Constabulary regarding this
OL,10,Fofficer, and has instructed the force
OL,11,Fto carry out an investigation into the
OL,12,Fofficer's conduct.
OL,14,FA spokesman for Durham Constabulary
OL,15,Fsaid: "Durham Constabulary can confirm
OL,16,Fthat a serving officer has been
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of rape.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
