PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784906303
OL,3,CPolice officer arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof rape
OL,6,F"The officer was arrested and
OL,7,Fimmediately suspended earlier this
OL,8,Fmonth while a criminal investigation
OL,9,Fwas launched by the force's
OL,10,FProfessional Standards Department. He
OL,11,Fhas since been released on bail while
OL,12,Fenquiries continue."
OL,14,FAn IOPC spokesperson said: "We can
OL,15,Fconfirm we received a referral from
OL,16,FDurham Constabulary after an officer
OL,17,Fwas arrested for a serious sexual
OL,18,Foffence.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
