OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784906303
OL,3,CPolice officer arrested on suspicion
OL,4,Cof rape
OL,6,F"Following a careful review of the
OL,7,Favailable information, we instructed
OL,8,Fthe force to carry out an
OL,9,Finvestigation into the officer's
OL,10,Fconduct."
